WEBVTT

1
00:21:45.480 --> 00:21:48.380 
还有很多延绵的山脉和峡谷
There are sprawling mountain ranges and canyons, too.

2
00:21:48.410 --> 00:21:51.050 
我们现在进入马里亚纳海沟
We've now entered the Marianas Trench,

3
00:21:48.410 --> 00:21:55.720 
海沟地处北太平洋西方海床 海沟底部于海平面下之深度 远胜珠穆朗玛峰海平面上之高度

4
00:21:51.080 --> 00:21:52.820 
地球上最深的峡谷
the deepest canyon on Earth,

5
00:21:52.850 --> 00:21:55.720 
超过1万米的深度
more than ten kilometers deep.

6
00:21:55.750 --> 00:21:58.690 
它形成构造力将海床推挤到
It formed when tectonic forces pushed the seabed

7
00:21:58.720 --> 00:22:00.690 
相邻的大陆板块下
under the adjoining continental plate.

8
00:22:00.730 --> 00:22:03.130 
上过月球的人
More people have walked on the Moon

9
00:22:03.160 --> 00:22:05.730 
比下来这里的多
than have ever been down here.

10
00:22:05.760 --> 00:22:10.000 
这里的压力达到了每平方英寸8吨
The pressure here is a crushing eight tons per square inch.

11
00:22:10.040 --> 00:22:12.200 
这样的深度
Being this deep in the ocean

12
00:22:12.240 --> 00:22:15.910 
就像是50架波音747叠在一起
is like having 50 jumbo jets stacked on top of you.

